# Weather Dashboard

A responsive and real-time weather dashboard built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript** with the **OpenWeatherMap API**.  
The application displays current weather conditions, temperature, humidity, wind speed, and a 5-day weather forecast with animated weather icons.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Real-time weather updates
- Search weather by city name
- Current temperature display
- Humidity and wind speed details
- 5-day weather forecast
- Dynamic weather icons
- Responsive and modern UI
- API integration using OpenWeatherMap

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- REST API
- OpenWeatherMap API

