## ▶️ How to Run

1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open the project folder
3. Create an API key from OpenWeatherMap
4. Add your API key inside `script.js`

```javascript
const apiKey = "YOUR_API_KEY";
```

5. Run the `index.html` file in your browser

